title: RoboSat.pink: Deep Learning Computer Vision patterns extraction at scale
abstract:
RoboSat.pink, a Deep Learning Computer Vision framework for GeoSpatial Imagery, allow you to perform at scale:

  • DataSet Quality Analysis
  • Change Detection highlight
  • Features extraction

This presentation will focus on the latests enhancements of RoboSat.pink, and mainly on:

  • How we increase again pattern recognition accuracy, even with unconsistents labels
  • How we speed up the whole process, and allow to scale even on large areas
  • New hot features
